665
00:48:41,984 --> 00:48:44,984
悔やみながら 決めればいいさ
while regretting, I just have to decide.

666
00:48:44,984 --> 00:48:48,984
君がくれた 言葉ひとつ
With the single word you gave me,

667
00:48:48,984 --> 00:48:51,984
戸惑いは消え去り
my hesitation vanished.

668
00:48:52,984 --> 00:48:57,984
からっぽだった 僕の部屋に 光が射した
A light shone into my empty room.

669
00:48:58,984 --> 00:49:05,984
見上げた大空が 青く澄み切って行く
The sky I looked up at is clearing into a brilliant blue.

670
00:49:06,984 --> 00:49:11,984
閉ざした 窓を 開く事を決めた
I decided to open the window I had closed.

671
00:49:12,984 --> 00:49:16,984
自分を 世界さえも
Myself, and even the world,

672
00:49:16,984 --> 00:49:19,984
変えてしまえそうな
it seems I can change them.

673
00:49:20,984 --> 00:49:23,984
瞬間は
That moment

674
00:49:23,984 --> 00:49:27,984
いつもすぐそばに…
is always right beside me...

675
00:49:48,984 --> 00:49:51,984
夢見てた、夢
The dream I was dreaming,

676
00:49:52,984 --> 00:49:56,984
果て無き遠く
was endlessly far away.

677
00:49:56,984 --> 00:50:00,984
乾いた日々の
Of these dry days,

678
00:50:00,984 --> 00:50:03,984
空色・手の中
the sky color is in my hands.

679
00:50:04,984 --> 00:50:08,984
等間隔 音の中で試行錯誤
Trial and error in the evenly spaced sounds.

680
00:50:08,984 --> 00:50:14,984
時間・間隔の無い空間 ah
A space without time or interval, ah

681
00:50:14,984 --> 00:50:17,984
等身大 音をたてて
Life-sized, making a sound,

682
00:50:17,984 --> 00:50:19,984
僕の顔、造って行く
I create my own face.

683
00:50:20,984 --> 00:50:23,984
キレイに、片方だけ
Beautifully, just one side.

684
00:50:42,984 --> 00:50:44,984
行けどもけものみち
Though I walk this beast's path,

685
00:50:44,984 --> 00:50:46,984
獅子よ虎よと吠え
I roar like a lion and a tiger.

686
00:50:46,984 --> 00:50:48,984
茜射す空の
In the madder-red sky,

687
00:50:48,984 --> 00:50:50,984
彼方にまほろば
beyond lies a paradise.

688
00:50:50,984 --> 00:50:52,984
幽囚の孤獨に
In the loneliness of confinement,

689
00:50:52,984 --> 00:50:54,984
彷徨う青春は
my youth wanders.

690
00:50:54,984 --> 00:50:57,984
弱さと怒りが姿無き敵ですか
Are weakness and anger my formless enemies?

691
00:50:58,984 --> 00:50:59,984
父よ 未だ我は
Father, I am still...

692
00:50:59,983 --> 00:51:00,983
未だ我は
I still

